{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01Pd7aZNjNSWAkpNdNF1iyzq","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_013quVZapex2pGR1yUvDBNko","name":"Agent","input":{"description":"Session retrospective","prompt":"Run a session retrospective for the current sprint session.\n\nSprint status: _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/sprint-status.yaml\nSession issues log: _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md\nCost report: Run `codeharness stats --save` to generate the cost report. Read `_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/cost-report.md` and include cost analysis in the retrospective.\n\nCRITICAL: Read the session issues log FIRST. This file contains real problems from this session and prior sessions today.\n\nThis was a NO-OP session — all 74 stories across 16 epics were already `done`. The only work was fixing state corruption (stories 16-5 through 16-8 reverting to `review` for the 9th time today).\n\nKey issues to analyze:\n1. The recurring state corruption bug — ralph's state reconciliation keeps overwriting story statuses from `done` back to `review`. This has happened 9 times today. This is the #1 priority bug.\n2. Token waste — each no-op session that just fixes state corruption costs API tokens for zero productive work.\n\nProduce a retrospective covering:\n1. Session summary — no new stories attempted, only state fix\n2. Issues analysis — the state corruption root cause\n3. Cost analysis — from the cost report, emphasize wasted spend on no-op sessions\n4. What went well — sprint is complete (all 74 stories done)\n5. What went wrong — state corruption recurring 9 times\n6. Lessons learned — need to fix reconciliation before next sprint\n7. Action items — fix the state reconciliation bug\n\nWrite the retrospective to _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-27.md. If it already exists, append to it with a `---` separator and timestamp.\n\nDo NOT ask the user any questions — proceed autonomously.\nDo NOT run git commit. Do NOT run git add. Do NOT modify sprint-status.yaml.","subagent_type":"general-purpose"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":121,"cache_read_input_tokens":45214,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":121},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"90decdda-ba60-48f6-a288-f3c67f5017cd","uuid":"5092ba6b-3e84-41e3-8cab-2909469a2a7a"}
